\int\frac{x^{2}}{(x+1)^{3}}dx
x=u-1 => \int\frac{(u-1)^{2}}{(u)^{3}}du = \int\frac{u^2-2u+1}{(u)^{3}}du = \int\frac{u-2}{(u)^{2}}du + \int\frac{1}{(u)^{3}}du
∫\dfrac{x^2}{(x+1)^3}dx
∫\dfrac{(u-1)^2}{(u)^3}du
∫\dfrac{u^2-2u+1}{(u)^3}du
∫\dfrac{1}{u}-\dfrac{2}{u^2}+\dfrac{1}{u^3}du
∫\dfrac{1}{u}du=ln(|u|)+c
